g.text: 0x00 | char* | source | Raw UTF-8 string buffer
0x08 | uint32_t | current | Cursor index for next byte
0x0C | uint32_t | start | Start of current lexeme

div.h1: CONSUMING: Returns current char and moves pointer
div.p: char = source[current] current += 1 if char == "\n": line += 1 column = 1 else: column += 1 return char
